10/23/80  request.compin

Syntax:  .ifi request         request_keyword "request name"
      OR .ifi rqst            request_keyword "request name"


Function:
This macro starts a new interactive subsystem (eg, qedx, read_mail, or
ol_dump) request description.


Macro action:
1) inserts 24pt. of white space
2) formats request_keyword and "request name" in 10pt Helvetica Bold
   Roman at the left margin
3) establishes request_keyword as the new right page header index slug


Notes:
1) If "request name" contains white space, it must be given as a quoted
   string.

(END)
